WHAT IT DOES?
=============
The purpose of this service APK is to provide file transfer service between two HotKnot devices.
During the file transfer, there will be a notification for show the file transferrring/receiving status.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
The MTK_HOTKNOT_SUPPORT feature optin should be true.

[Build Method]
make HotKnotBeam
or
mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/packages/apps/HotKnotBeam/

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
1.
It is launched after receiving com.mediatek.hotknotbeam.START intent which is sent from HotKnot APK.
2.
It is launched when the HotKnot setting is enabled or closed when the HotKnot setting is disabled.

